title: Factors Affecting Rate of Reaction
question: 哪些是 factor affect rate of reaction / faktor yang mempengaruhi kadar tindak balas
A: Temperature of reactants / Suhu bahan tindak balas
B: Concentration of reactants / Kepekatan bahan tindak balas
C: Size of solid reactants / Saiz bahan tindak balas berbentuk pepejal
F: Volume of reactants / Isipadu bahan tindak balas
G: State of matter of products / Keadaan jirim hasil tindak balas
H: Color of reactants / Warna bahan tindak balas
I: Density of reactants / Ketumpatan bahan tindak balas
J: Type of container used / Jenis bekas yang digunakan

question: Temperature of reactants / Suhu bahan tindak balas 越高，rate of reaction / kadar tindak balas 越
Concentration of reactants / Kepekatan bahan tindak balas 越高，rate of reaction / kadar tindak balas 越
Pressure / Tekanan 越高，rate of reaction / kadar tindak balas 越
Size of solid reactants / Saiz bahan tindak balas berbentuk pepejal 越大，rate of reaction / kadar tindak balas 越
Size of solid reactants / Saiz bahan tindak balas berbentuk pepejal 越小，面积越
Presence of catalyst / Kehadiran mangkin 会导致 rate of reaction / kadar tindak balas
